    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>腾讯云网址：<a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/">https://cloud.tencent.com/</a></p><h3 id="第一步，服务器设置"><a href="#第一步，服务器设置" class="headerlink" title="第一步，服务器设置"></a>第一步，服务器设置</h3><ul><li>如何部署，教程如下：</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_47343544/article/details/123012590">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_47343544/article/details/123012590</a></p><p>注：</p><p>公网地址：42.192.38.83</p><p>root密码：NICOnico123</p><ul><li>第一次root登录，教程如下：</li></ul><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/393589998">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/393589998</a></p><ul><li>mysql启动可能会报错，教程如下：</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43290288/article/details/118852753?spm=1001.2101.3001.6661.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-1-118852753-blog-103850782.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv4&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-1-118852753-blog-103850782.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv4&amp;utm_relevant_index=1">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43290288/article/details/118852753?spm=1001.2101.3001.6661.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-1-118852753-blog-103850782.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv4&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-1-118852753-blog-103850782.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv4&amp;utm_relevant_index=1</a></p><h3 id="第二步，网页部署"><a href="#第二步，网页部署" class="headerlink" title="第二步，网页部署"></a>第二步，网页部署</h3><ul><li>静态网页部署，教程如下：</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/DAZZPNB/article/details/119509246">https://blog.csdn.net/DAZZPNB/article/details/119509246</a></p><ul><li>使用nignx时，可能热重启没用，应该先将其关闭，再打开</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//stop</span><br><span class="line">nginx -s stop</span><br><span class="line">//start</span><br><span class="line">nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="第三步，域名设置"><a href="#第三步，域名设置" class="headerlink" title="第三步，域名设置"></a>第三步，域名设置</h3><ul><li>域名解析教程：</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ba476/article/details/123290616">https://blog.csdn.net/ba476/article/details/123290616</a></p><p>注：</p><p>域名为 <a href="http://www.fntl.club/">www.fntl.club</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
