  <entry>
    <title>pytorch安装</title>
    <link href="https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/09/23/pytorch%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97/"/>
    <id>https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/09/23/pytorch%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8C%97/</id>
    <published>2022-09-23T05:10:35.832Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-23T05:12:02.845Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1，先下载anaconda </p><p><a href="http://www.anaconda.com/">www.anaconda.com</a></p><p>进行换源</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/free/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建一个虚拟环境</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create -n pytorch python=3.9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>激活虚拟环境</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">activate pytorch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2，然后有独显的话查看最高支持什么版本的cuda，去cuda安装对应版本</p><p>注：选择CUDA版本，要么10.2要么11.3要么11.6</p><p>教程网址如下：</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Elon15/article/details/125678410">https://blog.csdn.net/Elon15/article/details/125678410</a></p><p>3，安装pytorch：<a href="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/">https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/</a></p><p>装pytorch时选择自己安装的对应cuda版本</p><p>选择stable(1.12.1)–windows–pip—python–CUDAxx.x，然后复制该语句</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip3 install torch torchvision torchaudio --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu113</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>粘贴到anaconda中</p><p>4，在anaconda prompt下激活虚拟环境后，安装官网底下的pip代码，安装好后，进入pycharm中，在右下角环境中设置成这个虚拟环境，然后就ok了</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_61405201/article/details/125717678">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_61405201/article/details/125717678</a></p><p>注：选择对应的虚拟环境中的python.exe文件</p><p>如，pytorch文件夹下的python.exe文件</p><p>验证代码</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> torch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">flag = torch.cuda.is_available()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(flag)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ngpu= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Decide which device we want to run on</span></span><br><span class="line">device = torch.device(<span class="string">&quot;cuda:0&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (torch.cuda.is_available() <span class="keyword">and</span> ngpu &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="string">&quot;cpu&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(device)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">cuda:<span class="number">0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
