  <entry>
    <title>git使用</title>
    <link href="https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/08/19/git%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/"/>
    <id>https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/08/19/git%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</id>
    <published>2022-08-19T02:32:11.044Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-22T07:00:09.232Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="git使用"><a href="#git使用" class="headerlink" title="git使用"></a>git使用</h1><p>初始化仓库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>工作区 –》 暂存区 </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：. 是通配符</p><p> 暂存区  –》 厂库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git commit -m &#x27;注释&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看状态</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看提交记录</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git-log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>版本退回</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git reset --hard 数字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看分支</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建并切换分支</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git checkout -b 分支名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分支合并</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git merge 分支名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>切换分支</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git checkout 分支名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>clone到本地仓库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone 网络地址 本地文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>拉取远程仓库修改并合并</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git pull</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>推送本地修改到远程仓库</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push [--set-upstream] origin 分支名</span><br><span class="line">例：</span><br><span class="line">git push --set-upstream origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：–set-upstream 表示绑定 </p><p>当前分支绑定到 远程master</p>]]></content>
    
    
