  <entry>
    <title>ryu+mininet血泪教训</title>
    <link href="https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/08/19/ryu+mininet%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%A1%80%E6%B3%AA%E6%95%99%E8%AE%AD/"/>
    <id>https://nicolikerest.github.io/2022/08/19/ryu+mininet%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%A1%80%E6%B3%AA%E6%95%99%E8%AE%AD/</id>
    <published>2022-08-19T02:32:07.750Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-22T07:00:09.245Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ryu-mininet血泪教训"><a href="#ryu-mininet血泪教训" class="headerlink" title="ryu+mininet血泪教训"></a>ryu+mininet血泪教训</h1><p>使用的是<strong>ubantu20版本</strong>，因为ryu后面的一些功能不支持python2，之前使用的ubantu16不支持python3，进行了重装</p><ul><li>ubantu安装教程</li></ul><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/355314438">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/355314438</a></p><h2 id="ryu问题-—版本ryu4-34"><a href="#ryu问题-—版本ryu4-34" class="headerlink" title="ryu问题 —版本ryu4.34"></a>ryu问题 —版本ryu4.34</h2><ul><li>安装参考链接：</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_42282103/article/details/126273926">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_42282103/article/details/126273926</a></p><ul><li>注：pip install -r tools&#x2F;pip-requires很容易安装失败，使用清华的镜像源</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43527191/article/details/108059276">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43527191/article/details/108059276</a></p><p>在命令后添加参数<code>-i &lt;镜像源地址&gt;</code>，如：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pip install -r tools/pip-requires -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>pip安装失败 — 网络问题</li></ul><p>注：进行换源，换阿里源直接起飞</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_62529383/article/details/124004470">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_62529383/article/details/124004470</a></p><h2 id="mininet问题"><a href="#mininet问题" class="headerlink" title="mininet问题"></a>mininet问题</h2><ul><li>运行miniedit.py时报错<strong>ImportError: No module named mininet.log</strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/fjlinww/p/13388427.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/fjlinww/p/13388427.html</a></p><ul><li>报错：“ImportError No module named setuptools</li></ul><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_37774696/article/details/84328916">https://blog.csdn.net/m0_37774696/article/details/84328916</a></p><p>setuptools下载地址：<a href="https://pypi.python.org/packages/1d/c0/57c129132059297460922eec3cabf3016e792455adf9db8c5b144db67d69/setuptools-21.0.0.zip#md5=1da14a897449567b4e151d7461a0c829">https://pypi.python.org/packages/1d/c0/57c129132059297460922eec3cabf3016e792455adf9db8c5b144db67d69/setuptools-21.0.0.zip#md5=1da14a897449567b4e151d7461a0c829</a></p><h2 id="未解决问题"><a href="#未解决问题" class="headerlink" title="未解决问题"></a>未解决问题</h2><p>在NAT模式下，主机不能访问虚拟机，虚拟机可上网</p><p>改为仅主机模式，可以访问虚拟机，虚拟机不可上网</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
